his notice only applies to internal shortlinks that render post content directly. External shortlinks are not affected.'=>'此通知僅適用於直接呈現帖子內容的內部短連結。外部短連結不受影響。','Notice Messages'=>'通知消息','Default redirection method for shortlinks'=>'短連結的預設重定向方法','Mark links as sponsored content'=>'將連結標記為贊助內容','Prevent search engines from following links'=>'防止搜尋引擎跟隨連結','Pass URL parameters to target links'=>'將URL參數傳遞給目標連結','Secure your shortlinks'=>'保護您的短連結','Users must enter a password to redirect to the target link.'=>'使用者必須輸入密碼才能重定向到目標連結。','Default Password'=>'預設密碼','Default password for protected links'=>'受保護連結的預設密碼','This password will be used for links that have password protection enabled via global settings. Passwords are case sensitive.'=>'此密碼將用於通過全域設定啟用密碼保護的連結。密碼區分大小寫。','Set an expiration date and time for shortlinks'=>'為短連結設置到期日期和時間','Select the date when this shortlink should stop working'=>'選擇此短連結應停止運作的日期','Select the time when the shortlink should expire'=>'選擇短連結應到期的時間','Revisions'=>'修訂','Revision Link Visibility'=>'修訂鏈接可見性','When enabled, revision shortlinks will appear in the "All Shortlinks" table based on the behavior you configure below.'=>'啟用後，修訂短鏈接將根據您在下面配置的行為出現在「所有短鏈接」表中。','When Revision is Created'=>'當修訂創建時','When Revision is Created or Link is First Used'=>'當修訂創建或鏈接首次使用時','Show Shortlink in Revision Table'=>'在修訂表中顯示短連結','Display shortlink column when viewing revisions in PublishPress Revisions.'=>'在 PublishPress 修訂中查看修訂時顯示短連結列。','Revision Visibility for Visitors'=>'訪客的修訂可見性','Allow logged-out visitors to view revision content via shortlinks.'=>'允許登出訪客通過短連結查看修訂內容。','By default, PublishPress Revisions blocks visitors from viewing revision previews. When enabled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'默認情況下，PublishPress 修訂會阻止訪客查看修訂預覽。啟用後，修訂短鏈接將直接為登出訪客呈現修訂內容，而不是重定向到預覽 URL。','Dummy'=>'虛擬','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'尚未配置任何文章類型。點擊 "添加文章類型" 開始使用。','Add Post Type'=>'添加文章類型','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'日誌條目已成功刪除。','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d 筆日誌條目已成功刪除。','All logs have been cleared.'=>'所有日誌已被清除。','Title'=>'標題','Details'=>'詳細信息','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'您確定要刪除這條日誌條目嗎？','View Analytics'=>'檢視分析','Tablet'=>'平板電腦','Mobile'=>'手機','Desktop'=>'桌面','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s 來自 %2$s 於 %3$s 訪問','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s 於 %2$s 訪問','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'來自 %1$s，訪問於 %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'訪問於 %s','via %s'=>'通過 %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'編輯短鏈接設置','This post is in {status} status. It will become visible to the public on {date}.'=>'此貼文處於 {status} 狀態。它將於 {date} 變為對公眾可見。','Target url not found.'=>'找不到目標網址。','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'無效的 URL 協議。僅允許 http、https、ftp、ftps 和 mailto。','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'無法創建微型標識。','Shortlink will appear here'=>'短連結將在此顯示','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'輸入一個長 URL 並製作短鏈接','Long URL'=>'長網址','Create Shortlink'=>'創建短鏈接','Reset Today\'s Analytics'=>'重置今天的分析','Reset Week\'s Analytics'=>'重置本週的分析','Reset Month\'s Analytics'=>'重置本月的分析','Reset Year\'s Analytics'=>'重置本年的分析','Are you sure you want to reset the analytics for this period? This action cannot be undone.'=>'您確定要重置此期間的分析嗎？此操作無法撤銷。','Today'=>'今天','Last 7 Days'=>'過去 7 天','Last 1 Month'=>'過去 1 個月','Last 1 Year'=>'過去 1 年','If you like %1$s please leave us a %2$s rating. Thank you!'=>'如果您喜歡 %1$s，請給我們留下 %2$s 評分。謝謝！','About'=>'關於','Documentation'=>'文檔','Contact'=>'聯絡','Download QR Code'=>'下載 QR 碼','We have developed extensions for the below browsers.'=>'我們已為以下瀏覽器開發擴展。','Click on your preferred one to Download the extension.'=>'點擊您偏好的選項以下載擴展。','Download the Extension'=>'下載擴展','Need PublishPress Shortlinks Support?'=>'需要 PublishPress 短連結支援嗎？','If you need help or have a new feature request, let us know.'=>'如果您需要幫助或有新的功能請求，請告訴我們。','Request Support'=>'請求支援','Detailed documentation is also available on the plugin website.'=>'詳細文檔也可在插件網站上獲得。','View Knowledge Base'=>'查看知識庫','This plugin can be deleted.'=>'此插件可以被刪除。','Copied.'=>'已複製。','This setting is inherited from global settings. Choose another option to override it for this shortlink.'=>'此設定繼承自全域設定。選擇其他選項以覆蓋此短連結。','Working...'=>'正在工作...']];